text: Ahrar Vocational School (Persian:هنرستان فنی حرفه ای احرار) (also known as Ahrar High School) is public 3-year single-sex vocational school located in Tehran Province, Iran. Students study software, computer networking, and accounting. == See also == * List of schools in Iran * Education in Iran * Lists of schools by country == References == Category:Vocational schools Category:Schools in Tehran Category:Boys' schools in Iran Category:Iranian school stubs
